ncrease hypotensive and CNS effects.', 'Synergism', 'Although often safe and effective, caution is advised during coadministration of MAOIs and phenothiazines, especially during the first few weeks of treatment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/160197/', '', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', '', 1767369485);
